title: The best Locksmith services in the Cincinnati Metro area
name: The best Locksmith services in the Cincinnati Metro area

properties.name: Available Locksmith Cincinnati - Residential & Foreclosure Lock Replacement
properties.description: Posted by Frnkgold 1232 W Kemper Rd #154, Cincinnati, 45240, OHMy wife and I came out from the movies the other night and when I tried to get the car started I managed to break the key in the ignition. We found Available Locksmith Cincinnati - Residential & Foreclosure Lock Replacement and gave them a call (513) 297-1150. The girl we spoke with over the phone was lovely, I explained what had happened and she assured me that the technician would be able to help. The sent someone out right away. The tech arrived and after some fiddling around he fixed the ignition and gave us a new key on the spot. Given the hour I was quite impressed they were able to help so quickly. The price matched the quote on the phone, and the tech even suggested that we take the car to the dealership to have it looked at in the morning. All in all quite impressive.

properties.name: Available Locksmith Covington- Commercial & Home Lock Re-Key
properties.description: Posted by Frnkgold P.O. Box 15551, Covington, 41015, KYWe came home for a weekend up at the cottage and right away noticed something was wrong. Someone had tried to break into the house while we were away. Thankfully they weren’t successful however the managed to completely destroy the front door lock in the process. We called Available Locksmith Covington- Commercial & Home Lock Re-Key at (937) 482-0050. They were able to send someone over right away to install a new lock, they even had one in stock that matched the front door! They were fast, efficient, and the price was reasonable!
